T02TD2429E:46a-1: aa sambandha sarga drishtha n'a ma /
T02TD2429E:46a-3: zhen med kyi lta ba zhes bya ba /
T02TD2429E:46a-5: srid pa gsum gyi rgyu las 'di //
T02TD2429E:46a-6: dpa' bo bdag gi dkyus sar thungs //
T02TD2429E:46a-7: bde gshegs lnga yi rta la zhon //
T02TD2429E:46a-8: rta pa bdag 'dra'i dpa' bo ni //
T02TD2429E:46a-9: 'jig rten na ni yod ma yin //
T02TD2429E:46a-10: brgyugs pas dug gsum rta rgod btul //
T02TD2429E:46a-11: lha chen bzhi yi sga yis bstad //
T02TD2429E:46a-12: shes rab thabs kyis srab tu bcug / rta pa bdag 'dra'i dpa' bo ni //
T02TD2429E:46a-13: 'jig rten na ni yod ma yin //
T02TD2429E:46a-14: brgyugs pas dug gsum rta rgod btul //
T02TD2429E:46a-15: nyon mongs bcu yi gsos cig byin //
T02TD2429E:46a-16: lta drug dbus kyi bres su bcug //
T02TD2429E:46a-17: brgyugs bas dug gsum rta rgod btul //
T02TD2429E:46a-18: rta pa bdag 'dra'i dpa' bo ni //
T02TD2429E:46a-19: 'jig rten na ni yod ma yin //
T02TD2429E:46a-20: bla ma lung gi ral gri thogs //
T02TD2429E:46b-0: @46b tshangs pa'i gnas drug steng du 'gro //
T02TD2429E:46b-1: rta pa bdag 'dra'i dpa' bo ni //
T02TD2429E:46b-2: 'jig rten na ni yod ma yin //
T02TD2429E:46b-3: brgyugs pas dug gsum rta rgod btul //
T02TD2429E:46b-4: phyogs bcu dag tu brgyugs pas kyang //
T02TD2429E:46b-5: de yi rta rjes mngon pa med //
T02TD2429E:46b-6: rta pa bdag 'dra'i dpa' bo ni //
T02TD2429E:46b-7: 'jig rten na ni yong ma yin //
T02TD2429E:46b-8: brgyugs pas dug gsum rta rgod thul //
